messages.message:
*Update: mypy should now work in CI*.

The fix was merged here: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/32745

If you have any outstanding Python PRs, please rebase off of master, or ensure you run `make test` on any modules you touched before merging in your PR to prevent accidentally breaking other engineers’ builds.

There were a handful of type errors that worked their way into master over the last month as a result of this bug; I tagged the relevant commits/people in my PR, please take a sec to fix up those errors so we can make sure there aren’t any lingering type errors :slightly_smiling_face: thanks all!
